question.query: what assets are being discussed on twitter

steps.text: Do you mean cryptocurrency assets (coins/tokens) being talked about on Twitter/X? If so, what timeframe and format do you want — e.g. top 10 most-mentioned in the last 24 hours, trending by engagement (likes/retweets), or a snapshot of current hashtags? I can pull live social-trend data (LunarCrush/TheTIE/Santiment/CoinGecko) and give a ranked list. Which would you prefer?
